OL,3,COperation Bass established to tackle
OL,4,Cspike in car and bike thefts
OL,6,FGuernsey Police have kickstarted a
OL,7,Ftargeted operation to counteract a
OL,8,Fspike in opportunist car and bike
OL,9,Fthefts.
OL,11,FOperation Bass sees officers actively
OL,12,Fpatrolling car parks to identify
OL,13,Fvehicles that are either unlocked or
OL,14,Fvulnerable to theft.
OL,16,FIt comes as the number of thefts has
OL,17,Fincreased by 54% this year, with four
OL,18,Fvehicles reported as stolen in
OL,19,FGuernsey since January 2025.
