OL,3,COperation Bass established to tackle
OL,4,Cspike in car and bike thefts
OL,6,FMore than #40,000 worth of stolen
OL,7,Fbicycles have also been reported this
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FIt's hoped Operation Bass will raise
OL,11,Fawareness among residents and also
OL,12,Fdeter opportunist thieves.
OL,14,FPC Mike Simmonds explains: "We're very
OL,15,Fkeen for people to understand that
OL,16,Fwe're not blaming people for their own
OL,17,Fmisfortune if they are a victim of
OL,18,Fcrime.
