OL,3,COperation Bass established to tackle
OL,4,Cspike in car and bike thefts
OL,6,F"At the same time, it's to emphasise
OL,7,Fthat we could all be doing more to
OL,8,Fraise minimum standards of security on
OL,9,Fthe island."
OL,11,FITV News joined the police on patrol
OL,12,Fto understand the scale of the issue.
OL,14,FIn that time, police officers found
OL,15,Feight vehicles unlocked within ten
OL,16,Fminutes.
OL,18,FOne car had a high-end pedal cycle and
OL,19,Friding gear in the boot, with the key
OL,20,Fleft in the vehicle's front.
