OL,4,Cspike in car and bike thefts
OL,6,FAt Beau Sejour, police found four out
OL,7,Fof eight bikes left there were
OL,8,Fcompletely insecure.
OL,10,FPolice say that the campaign also
OL,11,Fhopes to prevent crime from taking
OL,12,Fplace in the first instant.
OL,14,FPC Simmonds explains: "One gentleman
OL,15,Fhad left the van unsecured with his
OL,16,Fproperty in the back and he'd also
OL,17,Fleft his keys in the ignition.
