OL,6,F"We called him, he came down, and for
OL,7,Flack of a better term, he gave us an
OL,8,Fearful to the effect of 'have you not
OL,9,Fgot anything better to do? Are you not
OL,10,Fsolving real crime?'
OL,12,F"I told him 'We're trying our best to
OL,13,Fprevent crime rather than solving it
OL,14,Flater'.
OL,16,F"We will always do what we can for the
OL,17,Fpublic, but the more the public can do
OL,18,Fto help us the better."
